data.description: Home is being sold AS IS....... Looking for a peaceful retreat close to the heart of the city? Look no further!! This charming home is nestled in the Heatherton Heights neighborhood in Montgomery and boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Enjoy LVP flooring throughout the main areas, tile in the kitchen and bathrooms, soft carpet int he bedrooms and a beautiful tiled shower in the master bath. The fenced-in backyard and wired workshop provide plenty of space for someone to work on their hobbies. Plus, with easy access to restaurants, Maxwell AFB, and the interstate, this home offers both tranquility and convenience. Don't miss out on this must-see property - schedule your showing today!
